Line 322 in the java source file org.apache.log4j.netJMSAppender contains an 
extra ";".  This will cause a compilation error under JDK1.4.

\src\java\org\apache\log4j\net\JMSAppender.java:332
: unreachable statement
    [javac]     return urlPkgPrefixes;;
    [javac]                           ^
    [javac] 1 error

Replace

321  String getURLPkgPrefixes( ) {
322    return urlPkgPrefixes;;
323  }

with 

321  String getURLPkgPrefixes( ) {
322    return urlPkgPrefixes;
323  }


I downloaded the package from http://jakarta.apache.org/log4j/jakarta-log4j-
1.2.6.zip, which is linked from 
http://jakarta.apache.org/log4j/docs/download.html
